EntryPointStatus EntryPointStatus Enum

Definition

Namespace:
Assembly:
System.Fabric.dll

Specifies the status of the CodePackage EntryPoint deployed on a node.

Edit

In this Article

public enum EntryPointStatusPublic Enum EntryPointStatus

Fields

Invalid Invalid

The status of the entry point is unknown or invalid.
Pending Pending

The entry point is scheduled to be started.
Started Started

The entry point was started successfully and is running.
Starting Starting

The entry point is being started.
Stopped Stopped

The entry point is not running.
Stopping Stopping

The entry point is being stopped.
